约谈了有关媒体单位、户外广告发布单位和广告行业协会召开了行政会议，要求各单位暂时停止发布槟榔广告。目前广州已经下线「和成天下」候车亭广告 70 余个，「湘潭铺子」公交车身广告 19 个，「张新发」公交车身广告 150 个，「口味王」公交车身广告 100 个。截至 3 月 18 日，全市媒体、户外广告均已停止发布槟榔广告。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4080ea2662269d366249add22e7e7f3f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/478469704"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IltaM8s7yhuVrEAMaCDY4NjA3Nzc2INPEw4gGMAA4L0Aucgk0Nzg0Njk3MDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1628665304.4987838", "card_id": "Q_475301627", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 58}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果「钱不是问题」，你会买什么房子，如何装修布置自己的家？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-5e3c3e37b8769bf01933e0f19644343e_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/475301627"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IltaM8s7yhuVrEAMaCDY3OTAyNzk2IOPJ/ocGMAI4RkAvcgk0NzUzMDE2Mjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1628665304.4991968", "card_id": "Q_473579252", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "11 月初预产期，待产包需要准备哪些东西？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "一枚上班没空玩手机的上班孕妈，只想当个伸手党，请问待产包要准备哪些必需品，顺便问问哪个牌子的好用！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/473579252"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IltaM8s7yhuVrEAMaCDY3NTE5Nzg5IMnH24cGMAA4LUAwcgk0NzM1NzkyNTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1628665304.4995384", "card_id": "Q_285212032", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3854}, "target": {"title_are